    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors met or exceeded the required level for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at this risk level. Validation results demonstrate RH < 1 at all five operating points with errors within acceptance criteria. The simulation team confirmed that the solver configuration used for validation (build-7-rc2) is the immediate predecessor to the released build (build-7), with no hemolysis-relevant changes in the patch delta; accordingly, the validation evidence is considered applicable to the production model configuration and the COU decision is Accepted.",
